stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> queued
  queued --> launching
  launching --> running
  running --> idle : 5 min no events
  running --> done : session ends normally
  running --> failed : process crashes
  idle --> running : new event received
  idle --> stuck : 15 min no events
  stuck --> running : new event received
  done --> [*]
  failed --> [*]
